Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:03.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,对地进入角度、速度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,各机检查对地进入系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT一号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT二号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:10.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT三号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT四号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:12.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT五号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.15,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT六号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,关上面部防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,第一话  对月高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这样不热吗  罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,啊  没人会发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,多多保重  基斯  罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:57.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙兰·多尔你也保重了\N罗兰你也别勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,谢谢你  基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没射中  格威少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你是故意放走它的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,野狼逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那小伙子没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不愧是我们的格威少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,保重了  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个孩子溺水了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:25.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,杰茜嘉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,杰茜嘉！森姆你去下游！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,森姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:33.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他的脸色好转了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,一定是为了追这东西才溺水的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,外来人流落至此并不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:16.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,杰茜嘉  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好的  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果不是你溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:51.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我们海姆家才不准你这种外来人进入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.77,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你还是不要接近他为好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,无意接受恩惠\N我也有些钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我知道  罗兰·塞亚克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我家收费很贵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那么  我做工还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你看过我的背囊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你不是也偷窥了我们洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,溺水了看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,比起我们姐妹俩\N你对这个更有兴趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,请还给我！那是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,怎么这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你今晚有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这个镇里有座海姆矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.87,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我准备去那里做工落脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,诶～ 原来你是有打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,海姆矿山…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里是海姆先生的家?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,纪夏莱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,应该付多少钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:13.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的很像迪安娜陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,本来为了参加成人式而清洁身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,却被你破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:25.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,已经请求父亲大人\N让你在矿山做工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:40.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道那条河的水流那么急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.51,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,所以我才溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,被你们救了  很感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很快过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是?  去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:07:59.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,汽车过不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,去西盖尔山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,去西盖尔山！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟我来 出发啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:32.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个是你姐姐吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:35.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,后年轮到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,小姐你们到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你们今晚不可以再上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他们要进行通宵的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也是15岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,外来人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂！ 罗兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:55.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,外来人不能再往上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,发现了会被赶下山的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,现在开始成人式的通宵祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,各位成年人请离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这就是WHITE DOLL吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成年人下山  从前面快点下山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:26.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,下山吧  喝到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:33.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真羡慕年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你们真大胆！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,快下山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,选择自己的舞伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂  姬艾尔  选我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾尔  选我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:57.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾尔今天真漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸的新型机  真厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.36,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,比一比吧  看看有多快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好  你看着吧  新型机的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:40.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很热啊  快点弄完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他在新竖井的升降台上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰  活干完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,海姆老爷要见你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,老爷要见我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,老爷听说你对机器很在行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这就是格威少爷的最新式汽车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个…  我是罗兰·塞亚克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,即使是轿车 也能像跑车一样快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,厉害！这里也有座位!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是格威少爷命人改装的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:28.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哇！全都闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姐姐  很厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,战斗机也需要吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在海上的战斗也需要考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果加利亚大陆进攻这里的话\N的确有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因此  必须继续增加产量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,进入其他领地的山区这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:50.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,也请考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:55.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,知道了  不过真的会开战吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:56.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,传闻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:01.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是  我想利用这次机会\N建立工业化社会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不愧是少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.02,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,继承家业的同时\N也打算发展新时代的产业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,既然在政治和外交都被老人家霸占\N我也只能做这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗…叫罗兰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰·塞亚克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你从今天起担任我们的见习司机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,私家车的司机吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.21,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,太好了  罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,要抓紧空闲时间学习  考上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成为莱因福特少爷创造新时代的帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个…  你头发的颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:38.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你头发的颜色\N跟被野狼袭击的少年一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,非常感谢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,当时没有杀掉它  我很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,托您的福\N我后来被这里的两位小姐救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.01,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,既然大家有缘\N就更应该努力学习以报答少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,太好了  罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是  新时代的学问很难的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是这样吧?  格威少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是的  但是令尊很器重「罗拉」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:16.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,今年我打算让他参加迟了两年的成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:17.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我能够参加吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:20.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟我一起吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我带来的新式汽车在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:26.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,想试试你的技术 「罗拉·塞亚克」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:27.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爷  看天上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个是市民军的飞行部队吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,昆先生是个天才飞机师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:40.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,部队将全部由那种最快的飞机组编而成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,踩油门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,等待温度计到中间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想邀请姬艾尔小姐你参加\N这个夏天在城堡举行的派对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在波斯托尼亚城堡吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:55.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,两位不反对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,怎么会!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:03.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,小女能在波斯托尼亚城堡\N开始社交生涯  是我们的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爷一直将「罗兰」称为「罗拉」?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,差劲  所以才称为「市民军」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有空的人到飞艇下集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大佐  可以上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,想去见少爷吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为他出资购买爸爸的飞机嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:55.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,胡说\N是我推荐了美雪爸爸的那部飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,少爷只不过是出钱罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,已经批量生产 不必担心数量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这辆车就拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,谢谢少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你的技术很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很期待  罗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,bye
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他叫「罗兰」吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:25.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是「罗兰」没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,人手不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂  别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,开动马达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,取下那边的锚钩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.54,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很快就出来 你在这里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:25.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:32.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我才不会陪姐姐买\N派对时戴的首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里是迎合暴发户品味的珠宝店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾尔小姐的品味很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰你总是称赞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你看来混得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,基斯你也不错嘛  在面包店工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:13.36,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙兰也在诺克斯市工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你跟芙兰也见过面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:18.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,去这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我在域辛镇的海姆家里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在诺克斯市工作的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,家乡的普通朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可以开车了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,昨晚的功课你做完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:36.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,被凯特老师斥责只会浪费时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,对不起  因为我有事情\N所以要提早下课
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要紧  下周见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:52.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾尔·海姆小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰 不在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原来你一直在那里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,咦?  朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:42.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,当然  基斯你也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他们在谈甚么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,搓面粉的感觉很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:50.54,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很好吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:55.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙兰·多尔呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,她说会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:01.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,啊  不会是女孩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:05.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,同乡的聚会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,基斯的面包很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,听说芙兰你在报社的印刷厂工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是啊\N油墨的气味根本洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:24.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个女人想罗兰吻她吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,话说回来\N现在有信心在地球活下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,住口！别说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:37.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不过啊\N我还以为在报社会第一时间得知消息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但完全没有月球的新闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,「加利亚大陆」进攻这里的传闻\N不就是指月球吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:46.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.57,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰  那东西怎样了?  没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,工作很忙  我没去看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:55.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT已经自动钻进山谷底部\N不会那么简单就被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在看什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他们三个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不过我有点担心地震
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你懂开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没错  你离得近  去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,说得轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,纪夏莱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,听说卡车要拿去修理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,方向反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.77,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,熄掉车头灯比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:02.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球是个非常好的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:08.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,快回来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球是个非常好的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:17.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大家 快点回来吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:33.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,微热尚未消退
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:39.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,少年低垂的眼帘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:45.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,凝望心海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:50.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,静静地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:56.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,新生    消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,皆为宿命钟摆的两端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:09.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,穿越挫折的黑暗所见的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,才是真正的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:25.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,随着黎明献给被遗忘的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:27.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:34.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,至高的爱就在这双稚嫩的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:41.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在域辛镇成为我的故乡当日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.28,0:23:45.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军的人看见「迪安娜回归军」  反应过激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:54.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,当石像「WHITE DOLL」崩塌时\N我也吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为机动战士出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:01.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,次回 Turn A高达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:02.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:04.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,起风了
